Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這裡...是哪裡...？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:30.40,Default JP,,0,0,0,,誰...？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:30.40,Default CN,,0,0,0,,誰...？
